g.aria-label: X-axis titled 'date (month)' for a discrete scale with 12 values: January, February, March, April, May, ending with December
Y-axis titled 'Mean of precipitation' for a linear scale with values from 0 to 6
X-axis titled 'temp_min (binned)' for a linear scale with values from −10 to 20
Y-axis titled 'temp_max (binned)' for a linear scale with values from −5 to 40
Symbol legend titled 'Count of Records' for size with values from 0 to 254
